name: System Roles should be a E20 feature
objective: System Roles should be a E20 feature

customFields.Priority P1 to P4: P4 - Low-Impact (Edge or unsuitable to repeat?)

inline.description:
1. On an E10 instance, login to System Console and check if System Roles page is not displayed under User Management section.
2. Similarly check for E0 and TE instance.
3. System Roles page should only be displayed on E20 instance.
inline.expectedResult: System Roles page should only be displayed on E20 instance and should not be displayed on E10, E0 and TE edition.
